node.text: Little flashback Friday for ya. Imagine today a privateer having a AMA Pro National # in the 20s. We operated on such a small budget got bikes from the shop. When I won the Supercross Suzuki put a hat on me which I thought did not make sense at all since they did not give me any support. Crazy times. I’m glad there’s all the extra things nowadays like social media to help get ahead.All we had back in the day was a few hundred bucks you would win from the AMA.  Must say we had a lot of fun that’s for sure ! If anyone has any old pictures of me from back in the day racing feel free to send them my way. Thx Shopdeegan38@gmail.com #FBF #race #mxhistory

node.text: Almost 10years in this game with my son Haiden. Many years many memories. The pay off happens daily with the time spent as family. As our kids could be other places doing other things. Remember only a few will win this week so make sure you enjoy the time spent either way. I never won a overall here but I do remember camping with my dad under the trees in the van. No AC but I didn’t care.  We ate concession food and used the camp showers . My dad never ever yelled at me after a race ( sometimes I wish he would of ) so all my memories are good. We all know we are spending a lot to be here so try not to pay to build bad memories in your kids minds. I can’t remember all the motos even tho it seems so important at the time. Either way good luck and the only thing I really regret is not taking enough pictures when I was here with dad. #Family #Racing @lorettalynnmx @ryneswanberg pics

node.text: In a sport that takes a lot of money to compete in its always cool to get creative with partners on new concepts to build room for logos that in return gets more support to the riders. Love the creativity of @methodracewheels ! I feel together this is just the tip of the iceberg of the cool things will be doing together. And this concept I’m sure it will make its way to the pro teams but it’s a honor to get to debut them on Haidens race bike @lorettalynnmx .  Different times now that kids are getting big exposure on the internet. Hopefully it brings more support to the Ams also.  Thx Method now let’s kick some ass!! #methodracewheels #road2lorettas #Dangerboys #Deegan #ride #race #wheels #moto

node.text: If you are truly into motocross and have been in it your whole life like we have . You will understand the magic of watching the top Riders max out on a super mini! It is something magical. I was the kid on the fence watching the greats like Brian Swink ,Jeff Emig, Buddy Antunez , Jimmy Button , Damon Bradshaw , Jimmy Gaddis, Chad Pederson  the list goes on! (Feel free to refresh my list)There was always something magical about watching these guys ride a bike that is way too fast for its chassis to the limit! I’m excited to watch my son and all the other kids shred this year @lorettalynnmx .  As this is his last ride before stepping up to the big bikes where the work truly begins. @dangerboydeegan enjoy these magical times as I’m still that kid watching from the fence .. Love you son. #minibike #shredders #road2lorrettas
